import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import Button from './Button'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"hello-world"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#hello-world"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Hello world`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Button} />
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<Button>hello</Button>`} __scope={{props,Button}}>
    <Button>hello</Button>
</Playground></MDXTag>
